data.description: Step into this stunning house that offers the perfect combination of convenience and luxury. Situated on a huge lot in a desirable location, this home provides easy access to schools and shopping, ensuring that all your needs are just a stone's throw away.  One of the highlights of this magnificent property is the first-floor master suite. It offers privacy and tranquility, allowing you to indulge in a true retreat within your own home. This master suite boasts ample space, a luxurious en-suite bathroom, and generous closet space, providing the ultimate oasis of comfort. Brand new hot water tank and furnace.   The massive lot surrounding this house is a true gem. Imagine endless possibilities for outdoor activities, from creating your own private garden oasis to hosting memorable gatherings.   The proximity to schools and shopping adds an incredible level of convenience.  Sold AS IS. BATVI
